Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 09 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button

When I select 'Urinary bladder trauma' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Bladderrupture' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bladder tamponade' checkbox is enabled

And 'Artifacts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Not sufficient bladder filling' checkbox is enabled

And 'Inserted bladder catheter' checkbox is enabled
And 'Double-j catheter right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Double-j catheter left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Bladderrupture' checkbox
Then 'Intraperitoneal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Extraperitoneal' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Bladder tamponade' checkbox
Then 'Blood clot' checkbox is enabled
When I select 'Blood clot' checkbox
Then 'Max. diameter ' input field is enabled
